snippet.title: The Downfall of Amber Heard
snippet.description:
The Downfall of Amber Heard

Nobody expected this was coming but Johnny Depp's attorneys claim that
never-before-seen body cam footage from the Los Angeles police department (LAPD) officers who responded to the second of two 911 calls proves that Johnny Depp did not have the violent altercation with his ex-wife! Moreover, it proves that Amber Heard lied about the alleged brawl that took place in May 2016. 

However, it's not the first time that Amber Heard lied. Let’s look back at the
following things: donating the entirety of the divorce settlement money to a
children’s charity, an abuse story that she stole from her former colleague, the ‘dogs story’, never hitting Johnny Depp, and many other things.

All about Amber Heard and Johnny Depp: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ocYczSAnwe4&list=PL-LyakzH3f2lqAYSUPCvC1b8oXVhqyTPG
